CAPE TOWN - The man who raped and murdered Franziska Blochliger has been sentenced to two life-terms in prison.Howard Oliver was sentenced to an additional 15 years for robbery.READ: Oliver guilty in Blochliger rape and murderOliver admitted to committing the crimes in the Western Cape High Court last week.He had previously denied raping and murdering the 16-year-old girl last year.The teenager's body was discovered shortly after she went missing while jogging in Tokai forest.eNCA